      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so if we go with a much higher thread count to minimize those gaps, does that create a more \"impenetrable\" barrier for microscopic particles? i just want to be sure that a dense weave actually provides a reliable shield against anything trying to penetrate the material during transit.",
